c0f7ba0807e491e0e2f3412d","tid":1629122,"uid":2719,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T07:55:28.000Z","msg":"上年柒婆夠話特首無能力推緊急法啦屌你老母！"},{"pid":"ab33e70120c05c32860e88699723eb839503484d","tid":1629122,"uid":36065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T07:55:50.000Z","msg":"姐係將會做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"845e2569a3bde251744284021930e3bc76023f87","tid":1629122,"uid":76263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T07:56:14.000Z","msg":"冇保證過唔充公香港人嘅錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b528e68fd872a455eec7e23ff8cbec38c81b198","tid":1629122,"uid":251414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T07:57:28.000Z","msg":"<strong>政府大狀余若海：立咗矇面法即刻少咗暴力</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1628828/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1628828/page/1</a> <br />\n他(余若海)指出，蒙面法於本月5日生效，而在當天警方沒有施放任何催淚彈，可見自蒙面法生效後，示威情況沒以往激烈和暴力，蒙面法不會引致更多暴力示威的情況。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>法律教授張達明聽日都出！比唒貼士個法律漏洞喺邊！</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1625845/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1625845/page/1</a> <br />\n戴上口罩，難道你就認不出我？<br />\n明天(星期日)下午，我會以此裝束走上港島街頭。我不忍心看見年輕人成為制度暴力的犧牲品，所以衷心希望明天香港人能站出來，以和平理性方式，讓政權看見民心所向。<br />\n戴上口罩，不是要「使用相當可能阻止識辨身份的蒙面物品」，而是要對政權倒行逆施、繞過立法會，以《緊急法》訂立《禁止蒙面規例》，作無聲抗議。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>十八區裝修 Google地標、指南</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1628610\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1628610</a><br />\n【目標選擇原則】<br />\n（１）對準政權：中共港共政權建築物、中聯辦物業、保皇黨議員物業、保皇黨辦事處、黨鐵及其他政權走狗建議優先處理<br />\n（２）先做主線：過多商舖目標導致失焦，觀感上容易變成無差別攻擊，容易被屈做打砸搶的真暴徒，前線亦會攰。因此未有嚴重傷害或出賣抗爭者的對象或紅資支線任務建議押後處理。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BKoqZ1R.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBKoqZ1R.jpg&h=4a38e16d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n利申：反對任何暴力！"},{"pid":"19c8c0218fc5c0a09d34f7011d093eb3ed944460","tid":1629122,"uid":217254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T08:00:03.000Z","msg":"提款管制呢？"},{"pid":"439184c392ba9daee1bf6b8c0ad5b3fe1d25edcf","tid":1629122,"uid":62116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T08:00:44.000Z","msg":"佢咁講就係引起大家討論之後去做 同緊急法個陣差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"389a1f0c8ea956f5e9795063e484f06c24336c97","tid":1629122,"uid":270619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T08:01:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://thumbs2.imagebam.com/da/77/ba/999ffd1322031301.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthumbs2.imagebam.com%2Fda%2F77%2Fba%2F999ffd1322031301.jpg&h=862f2436&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://thumbs2.imagebam.com/92/1d/3e/7309251322031308.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthumbs2.imagebam.com%2F92%2F1d%2F3e%2F7309251322031308.jpg&h=5256b343&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b6a00f93b8087b9bd62bb735ed82420750355c66","tid":1629122,"uid":270619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T08:02:01.000Z","msg":"[IMG]<a href=\"https://thumbs2.imagebam.com/da/77/ba/999ffd1322031301.jpg[/IMG\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthumbs2.imagebam.com%2Fda%2F77%2Fba%2F999ffd1322031301.jpg%5B%2FIMG&d=zkxump%2FGNOlz%2FwmZAqM4lJ1DrXAeA17tgS6Eh9jzous%3D&h=c3115319\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thumbs2.imagebam.com/da/77/ba/999ffd1322031301.jpg[/IMG</a><img src=\"https://thumbs2.imagebam.com/92/1d/3e/7309251322031308.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthumbs2.imagebam.com%2F92%2F1d%2F3e%2F7309251322031308.jpg&h=5256b343&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ffe1fabbdc90d43aa2483a11ad96754e24804cce","tid":1629122,"uid":159448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T08:08:18.000Z","msg":"可唔可以叫燒山比個方向"},{"pid":"f3298d55d4abbf82903efb73e18def85f47bd630","tid":1629122,"uid":67553,"lik